summary: This document is the Seventh Supplemental Indenture dated November 17, 2025, between Intercontinental Exchange, Inc. and Computershare Trust Company, N.A., establishing two new series of senior notes: 3.950% Senior Notes due 2028 and 4.200% Senior Notes due 2031, under the Base Indenture dated August 13, 2018. It outlines the terms and conditions for these notes, including definitions and specific provisions related to the issuance and management of the securities.
